@startuml seq_30_view_analytics
title Sequence Diagram: UC-30 View Analytics

actor Admin
participant "Admin Web" as Frontend
participant "Analytics Controller" as Controller
participant "Analytics Service" as Service
participant "User Repo" as UserRepo
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Community Repo" as CommRepo

Admin -> Frontend: Open Analytics Dashboard
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/admin/analytics
Controller -> Service: Get Dashboard Analytics
Service -> UserRepo: Validate Admin Access
UserRepo --> Service: Access valid

par Aggregate statistics concurrently
    Service -> UserRepo: Count total users & growth rate
    Service -> PostRepo: Count total posts & engagement
    Service -> CommRepo: Count total communities
    UserRepo --> Service: User stats
    PostRepo --> Service: Post stats
    CommRepo --> Service: Community stats
end

Service -> Service: Compile analytics report
Service --> Controller: Analytics Data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: Render charts and statistics UI
@enduml